msgstr ""

#: src/components/landing/FAQSection.tsx:46
msgid ""
"GlossBoss can load glossaries directly from WordPress.org for any plugin or "
"theme, browse the actual plugin source files via SVN, and use Google Gemini "
"to read your source code for context-aware translations — so the AI understa"
"nds where each string appears in your UI."
msgstr ""
"GlossBoss kan glossaries direct laden van WordPress.org voor elke plug-in of"
" thema, de daadwerkelijke bronbestanden van de plug-in bladeren via SVN en G"
"oogle Gemini gebruiken om je broncode te lezen voor contextbewuste vertaling"
"en — zodat de AI begrijpt waar elke string in je UI verschijnt."

#: src/components/landing/FAQSection.tsx:28
msgid ""
"GlossBoss combines the simplicity of Poedit with the collaboration features "
"of Crowdin — in the browser, with no install required. It supports three AI "
"translation providers instead of one, has deep WordPress integration with so"
"urce-code context, includes a full review workflow with threaded comments, s"
"yncs directly with GitHub and GitLab, and is open source."
msgstr ""
"GlossBoss combineert de eenvoud van Poedit met de samenwerkingsfuncties van "
"Crowdin — in de browser, zonder installatie. Het ondersteunt drie AI vertaal"
"aanbieders in plaats van één, heeft diepe WordPress-integratie met broncode "
"context, bevat een volledige reviewworkflow met discussiethreads, synchronis"
"eert direct met GitHub en GitLab, en is open source."

#: src/pages/PrivacyPage.tsx:333
msgid ""
"GlossBoss does not use tracking cookies. Authentication state is managed via"
" Supabase's session tokens stored in local storage. Analytics (PostHog) runs"
" in cookie-less mode using in-memory persistence. Analytics requests are rou"
"ted through a first-party proxy on our domain - no third-party tracking doma"
"ins are contacted from your browser."
msgstr ""

#: src/pages/index/IndexPageDialogs.tsx:215
msgid ""
"GlossBoss found QA issues in the current file. You can review them now or ex"
"port anyway."
msgstr ""
"GlossBoss heeft QA-problemen gevonden in het huidige bestand. Je kunt ze nu "
"bekijken of toch exporteren."

#: src/components/landing/OpenSourceSection.tsx:24
msgid ""
"GlossBoss is AGPL-3.0 licensed. Inspect the code, self-host it, or contribut"
"e. No vendor lock-in — your translations stay in standard PO and JSON format"
"s."
msgstr ""
"GlossBoss heeft een AGPL-3.0 licentie. Inspecteer de code, host het zelf, of"
" draag bij. Geen vendor lock-in — je vertalingen blijven in standaard PO- en"
" JSON-formaten."

#: src/pages/TermsPage.tsx:25
msgid ""
"GlossBoss is a browser-based translation editor for gettext and i18next tran"
"slation files. It provides a web-based editor for managing translations, wit"
"h optional cloud features including project hosting, team collaboration, and"
" machine translation integrations."
msgstr ""

#: src/pages/LicensePage.tsx:14
