"GlossBoss supports gettext PO/POT files and i18next JSON resources. These co"
"ver WordPress plugins and themes, React and JavaScript apps, and most open-s"
"ource projects."
msgstr ""
"GlossBoss ondersteunt gettext PO/POT-bestanden en i18next JSON-resources. De"
